{"type": "article", "id": 22185, "title": "可抚触卫衣", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-14T08:23:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143609ReEWZxSPDr7hBzt0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>恋人之间表达爱意的方式免不了亲密的身体接触，比如牵手，比如很多女生难以招架的摸头杀。来自纽约的设计师 Drew Stanley 想了个奇妙的招儿，利用常见的运动衫和 T 恤，在背部、肩部以及胸口等地方设计了一些诸如口袋、镂空细节的东西，像是一个微妙的邀请，让彼此靠得更近，体验肌肤之亲。我们承认镂空那个略略有点奇怪啦（尤其是男生打底就更奇怪了），不过，情人节嘛！买来，呃，情趣一下？如需购买，请尝试联系 drewstanley.contact@gmail.com.</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061436063p8FnUvZSrmeIdEO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143606o9KZcHrJYnS7wbIU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5953125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143607kt0Ge3DfRZH2lu9Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143607976rMfRNCxbThjIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143608Egvqkjo81bJATDPM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143608oXIkw4pJj13liTNL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.384\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}